o3smeasures.structures

Class ItemMeasured

  • java.lang.Object
    • o3smeasures.structures.ItemMeasured

  • public class ItemMeasured
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents the an item measured by the plug-in, that could be a package, a compilation unit or a method. It also records the measurement value, the mean, the parent item of the measure and all the children items.
    Since:
    13/07/2014
    Author:
    Mariana Azevedo
